relation: Darrow2 - #14Wrapping up their trip through Threed, Ness and friends hop on board the bus and head on over to Fourside. Well, that was the original plan, at least.

Darrow2 - #13 Coming back to Threed, Ness, Paula, and Jeff discover a few gifts waiting for them. Coincidentally, the man who currently owns Ness' painting always sleeps with one eye open from now on.
Darrow2 - #12 The third melody comes to Ness, and Jeff finds that running through Saturn Valley is probably his best option upon return.
Darrow2 - #11 With the Trillionage Sprout out of the way, our heroes move onto bigger and better things. Namely, Jeff actually being able to move again.
Darrow2 - #10 Although Trillionage Sprout is a tough customer, his eyes are loosely held on with some old glue.
